{
  "$comment": "Central icon registry for the Bifrost theme. Source of truth for: (1) every SVG partial available under themes/bifrost/templates/partials/icons/, (2) the semantic bindings that map slugs to icon IDs (used by macros/section-icons.html), (3) per-icon metadata for future audits — style family, original source, Iconify URL, viewBox, and where each icon is used. New icon procedure: drop SVG into partials/icons/, add an `icons` entry here, add a render branch in macros/section-icons.html. New binding: edit `bindings` and the relevant template.",
