    "stroked": "Hand-drawn thin outlines, currentColor stroke, typically 24x24 viewBox. Visually light.",
    "filled": "Bold filled silhouettes, currentColor fill, typically 256x256 or 512x512 viewBox. Visually heavy.",
    "mixed": "Stroked outline with a small filled accent (e.g. a dot in the middle)."
  },
